&lt;p&gt;Buy three of these, pair it with a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B01A02QFV0&quot;&gt;single-stand, triple monitor mount&lt;/a&gt; and get to work.  If you’ve got the budget for an upgrade, Dell’s &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.dell.com/ed/business/p/dell-u2414h/pd&quot;&gt;UltraSharp line&lt;/a&gt; is a worthy improvement.&lt;/p&gt;
