&lt;p&gt;I have a set of &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00CD1PTF0&quot;&gt;Bose Companions&lt;/a&gt; double-wired to my desktop as well as my laptop.  The notepad, cup of coffee and a Nalgene are permanent fixtures on my desk as well.&lt;/p&gt;
